{"tid":1681150,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"會員一鋪過入【懷疑五毛】","createTime":"2019-10-29T08:42:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-12T03:35:57.000Z","uid":163448,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"cc3f2e5bb1ed6dc1ccd150753e6025662fd05c34","tid":1681150,"uid":163448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T08:42:21.000Z","msg":"唔講咁多，去圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/09xq6uu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F09xq6uu.png&h=259a8e9d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BVr3S9v.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBVr3S9v.png&h=e2ec8695&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係咁吹獨立，又分化嘅仆街<br />\n我懷疑嘅只係想知係5毛定阿sir<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n五毛就唔該pro 啲<br />\n阿sir就<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e2d980c739315e09d7ccce28be2d4fa2e194982","tid":1681150,"uid":205162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T08:43:11.000Z","msg":"一早block左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f327d9dbb42d2bf531918267b443e5c91c30eaa","tid":1681150,"uid":136893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T08:50:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">記唔記得7、8月既時候，臨有行動前一日既連登，係充滿住遊行路線、離開方法、行動目的地既街坊整既攻略、仲有各種各樣既行動資訊整合，所有行動都係至小早半個月搞，有D 活動更加係會根據其重要性去調配，例如我記得葵青區遊行係推遲左成個月的。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n反思行動及行動數量<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">（極緊急！！！）等我教大家點再引發群眾熱情<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1680895\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1680895</a></span></span>"},{"pid":"a92db9f406edff4d5236826d151d50583644522e","tid":1681150,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T08:51:40.000Z","msg":"一早block左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.