hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1703944/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1703944/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>今日香港人是咪好嬲？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？ - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>聽朝準時返工表達不滿<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1690782/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1690782/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>宜家班勇武示威者癲到玩埋土製炸彈, 同工聯會暴徒有乜分別? 今次一次要割了 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/nVWEx2b.jpg\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1651704/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1651704/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>林鄭媽媽果然有計, 蒙面法一實施俾你班友玩幾日, 到今個星期加埋黨鐵宵禁, 呢個星期終於靜左 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>林鄭媽媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n,希望可以繼續落去還我正常生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1643169/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1643169/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>黃之鋒再次賣港- 德國演說 &quot; Hong Kong is Part of China &quot; - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/11/xelVBc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F11%2FxelVBc.png&h=c48ea686&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我地做咁多野都係晒鳩氣<br />\n一鋪俾佢搞灣<br />\n中共都屈你港獨之首啦, 咁你咪認撚左佢lor. 扮乜野呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔通你講句Hong Kong is Part of China就會俾你再返大陸咩<br />\n<br />\n睇下我地呢3個月不斷講Hong Kong is not china<br />\n晒鳩氣<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/sports/page/800/2015/11/18/54.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fsports%2Fpage%2F800%2F2015%2F11%2F18%2F54.jpg&h=b9eb8cb9&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1559448/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1559448/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n意見及舉報： <a href=\"http://lih.kg/1707551\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/1707551</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"cb4a12c7e123fd693d0c91a5ff8da16b8f3f1a2f","tid":1681150,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T18:59:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JFp2rPn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJFp2rPn.png&h=b7060aa9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1f945a3609aed16dc96dc2a0d97dc04344a6a69e","tid":1681150,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T19:00:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ikSb4Bq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FikSb4Bq.png&h=5149969a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"41237ddd4d5aea079204911303986cf7c2e42de7","tid":1681150,"uid":36551,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T19:25:57.000Z","msg":"唔洗懷疑，佢貼啲圖直情同facebook啲五毛一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edf72ac2efc3dee0aad7bae3f9ae497ab91f672f","tid":1681150,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T19:28:54.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f8863af8c0d17c740f17f95e9aaa3ebbd0abcf38","tid":1681150,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30